### Template for js webApp and solidity backend

## Commands
truffle init : initialize Project
change solidity version in truffle-config.js

In Ganache add the project config file via the contract tab.

truffle compile : compile code
if error due to compile version --> change compilers/solc/version in truffle-config.js
truffle migrate --reset : run migrations files and deploy contracts

truffle console : open ganache console

# In Ganache console --> JS
let instance = await Main.deployed()
migrate  : will compile and migrate
migrate --reset: will overwrite previous migration


# Python http server
python3 -m http.server
open http://localhost:8000 in browser


# intellijIDEA
intellij-idea-ultimate

## web App
get ABI from build/contracts/
or directly via : JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('../build/contracts/Migrations.json', 'utf8'))

